value: Indon, Salawati, New Guinea, Sorong, Waigeo, West Papuan Islands
NE Asia; winters SE Asia to Philippines and Indonesia
Breeds in Ussuriland, Japan and eastern China. In winter to Burma, Tenasserim and Malay Peninsula and Indo-Chinese countries, Philippines, Borneo, Celebes, Moluccas and New Guinea.
